gory:People from Vienna]]\n[[Category:French people of Austrian descent]]\n[[Category:Foreign volunteers in the Spanish Civil War]]\n[[Category:French Resistance members]]\n[[Category:Austrian Resistance members]]\n[[Category:Austrian Jews]]\n[[Category:Scholars of childhood]]\n[[Category:Anti-war activists]]\n[[Category:Anti\u2013nuclear weapons activists]]\n[[Category:Humanitarians]]\n", "name_user": "BerlinFR2503", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alfred_Brauner"}
